These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, baseball
There 2 different types of food: mango, cucumber
1. the person eating mango is in an even position##4
2. the person eating cucumber is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Sport   | baseball | golf |
| Food     | cucumber    | mango   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, japanese
City: hannover, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Nationality   | japanese | mexican        |
| City      | hannover  | edinburgh |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
City: paris, hannover
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| City   | hannover    | paris |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda |

