.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, photography
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby   | video-games      | photography |
| Game       | mah-jongg | billiard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
